Package: RCapsis
Type: Package
Title: Connect to 'CAPSIS' platform and Run Growth Simulations
Version: 0.0.1
Author: Mathieu Fortin, Canadian Wood Fibre Centre, Canadian Forest Service
Maintainer: Mathieu Fortin <mathieu.fortin.re@gmail.com>
Copyright: Her Majesty the Queen in right of Canada
Description: Makes it possible to connect to a local distribution of the 'CAPSIS' platform and to
    run some scripts from the 'R' environment. This package relies on 'J4R' for the connection to
    the 'Java' environment. 
Imports:
    J4R (>= 1.1.0)
